review:
I went to Dr.Rajesh for Vitamin-D prescription as I was diagnosed with Vitamin-D deficiency may be a reason for dry eyes after seeing earlier positive feedback in practo.
     As mentioned in feedback by vandana, he enquired me everything regarding my dry eyes problem. I felt very comfortable and at the same time he has given me so much of time (nearly half-an-hour) to explain my problem history. The good thing is till now I went to so many doctors but nobody has spent this much time with patients to find out the proper reason for a problem. So I highly recommend him from my side.. :)
    Will update my problem improvement once i am done with prescribed course..!!
